act.article:
2 Definitions. 

1 In these rules, unless the context 
otherwise requires, 

 a Act means the Passports Act, 1967 (15 of 1967); 
 b Mini-Passport Seva Kendra means a small passport application 
  processing centre under the Passport Seva Project; 
 c Passport Seva Kendra means a passport application processing centre 
  under the Passport Seva Project; 
 d Passport Seva Project means the public private partnership model 
  project to accept and process passport applications, issue of passport, 
  maintain data thereto and all other works connected therewith; 
 e  Schedule means the Schedule annexed to these rules; 
 f section means section of the Act; 
 g Service Provider means a person or entity which is awarded the 
  contract for implementing a Passport Seva Project. 

2 Words and expressions used herein and not defined, but defined in the Act 
shall have the meaning respectively assigned to them in the Act.
